  <brief_title>Lactobacillus Farciminis and Hyperalgesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of a Dialy Consumption of a Probiotic (Lactobacillus Farciminis) on Hyperalgesia in Response to Thermal Stimulation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
