  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We want to analyse a possible effect of o dialy consumption of Lactobacillus farciminis on a
      hyperalgesia on response to thermal stimulation. A comparaison of results before and after
      three weeks of treatment will be made.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
